                            <p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">上一篇文章我们介绍了定期寿险，今天就和大家分享一下加拿大几家大型保险公司的定期寿险比较。定期寿险产品，由于理赔标准很明确（也即身故即赔偿，两年内自杀除外），也没有现金价值，所以我们都会建议大家选择大一点的保险公司，毕竟承保能力强，理赔速度也会相对较快。这里我们专门选择了四家大的保险公司的产品，供您参考。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: white; background: #FF6969;">Canada Life</span><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: SimSun; color: white; background: #FF6969;">加拿大人寿</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">Canada Life是国字号的保险公司，成立于1847年，也是加拿大历史最悠久的保险公司。2020年1月1日，Canada Life, London Life和Great West Life合并成一个公司品牌，即Canada Life。接下来，我们看看Canada Life定期寿险的产品特点：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">产品种类</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T10：10年保费不变，申请年龄16岁到75岁（魁省申请年龄最小18岁）；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T20：20年保费不变，申请年龄16岁到65岁（魁省申请年龄最小18岁）；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T30：30年保费不变，申请年龄16岁到55岁（魁省申请年龄最小18岁）；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T65：保障保到65岁期间保费不变，申请年龄16岁到45岁（魁省申请年龄最小18岁）。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">保额上限</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">保额上限：</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">2000万。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">产品特色</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">1）Simple Protect，最便捷的申请方式，没有之一！！保额在200万以内，只需回答10-20个问题，15分钟内完成申请，且第一笔保费可以通过刷Visa、Master信用卡完成。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">2）Original Age Conversion。对于希望从定期保险转成终身保险的客人来说，Canada Life提供按照原来年龄的保费转换的机会。比如客人30岁申请的定期险保单，客人可以在35岁前按照30岁年龄的保费转成终身险，只需补齐这几年的保费及利息即可。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">3）附带Child term rider, 也即大人承保时可以附加一个最高保额2.5万的儿童险，最多可以保到65岁，价格也非常便宜。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">4）保额100万以内，年龄45岁以下，可以免体检。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: white; background: #FF6969;">Manulife</span><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: SimSun; color: white; background: #FF6969;">宏利人寿</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">Manulife宏利金融成立于1887年，由加拿大首任总理约翰.亚历山大.麦当劳创立，Manulife可以说是加拿大资产规模最大的保险公司，业务范围遍布美国、加拿大和亚洲，实力雄厚。目前总资产大约7800亿加币，拥有34000名员工和2800万的客户，其股票在多伦多，香港和纽约的证券市场交易。近年能达到月600亿加币的年收入，在美国的子公司为John Hancock。其定期寿险的产品如下：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">产品种类</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T10：10年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到70岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T20：20年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到60岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T65：保障保到65岁保费不变，申请年龄18岁到45岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T100：保到100岁，申请年龄60岁到85岁。<strong>独家！！</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">保额上限</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">保额上限：</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">2500万<strong>（实力杠杠的！！！）</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian;">产品特色</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">（</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">1）保额100万以内，年龄50岁以下，可以免体检。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">（</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">2）除了传统的定期寿险外，Manulife还提供一类特殊的定期寿险产品，名为Vitality，这是一项将健康管理与保险相结合的寿险产品。保费与健康相关活动的积分挂钩，会通过Vitality等级（铜级、银级、金级、白金级）来确定受保人下一年的保费。欲进一步了解，可以参考文章：</span><span style="color: black;"><a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDAxNDI3MA==&amp;mid=2247483918&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d8849d879931b4c9185fcabf54d3d89e&amp;chksm=fbeb415fcc9cc849426084ae36c3e2d507a42a8d70547e9a4c5a228b9ad8370a5b28eeb5dcc4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">与众不同的人寿保险：宏利保险</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">Vitality乐活计划</span></a></span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>独家！！</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">可以说，</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">Vitality是引导人们健康生活的新理念，是保险产品的创新。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: white; background: #FF6969;">Equitable Life</span><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: SimSun; color: white; background: #FF6969;">恒信人寿</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">恒信人寿公司成立于</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">1920年，2020年迎来100周年的庆典，总资产45亿加币，是没有上市的大型保险公司之一。恒信人寿的高性价比和未来的无限潜力让该公司在加拿大保险市场占有了相当重要的位置。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">产品种类</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T10：10年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到75岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T20：20年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到65岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">T30/65：保障30年或者保到65岁保费不变，申请年龄18岁到55岁。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">保额上限</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">保额上限：</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">1000万。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">产品特色</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">（</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">1） Joint first to die，如果受保人是夫妻联名承保（同一张保单承保两个受保人），第一人不幸离世即理赔，如果第二人在60天内随即离世（70岁以下），则可以理赔双倍保额。独家！！</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">（</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">2） 报销500元的丧葬咨询费用Bereavement Counseling Benefit。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: white; background: #FF6969;">Industrial Alliance</span><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: SimSun; color: white; background: #FF6969;">国联人寿</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">国联人寿成立于</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">1892年，目前资产约920亿加币，其业务遍布加拿大，明星产品如重大疾病保险占有率达到了百分之五十左右。2018年共接到保费一百亿加币。这家公司同时从美国市场收到了8.3个亿保费。其定期寿险的特点如下：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">产品种类</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">T10：10年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到70岁；</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">T20：20年保费不变，申请年龄18岁到70岁，可以保到90岁。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">保额上限</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">保额上限：</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">1000万。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">产品特色</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">1）Pick-a-term：投保人可以自由选择定期的时间，从10到40年均可，最高可以保到85岁。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; line-height: 150%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">（</span><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: DengXian;">2）儿童可以购买定期险，出生15天后即可购买，最多可以保到85岁。独家！！</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: SimSun; color: white; background: #FF6969;">价格比较</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">接下来，我们来对比一下各家的保费情况：</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">例一：客人男性，</span><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: black;">35岁，不吸烟，保额100万，标准保费比较如下（年保费，单位：加币）：</span></p>
